headline: Why Accenture Stock Flew Higher on Friday
summary: The only significant news item about Accenture (NYSE: ACN) Friday was a positive one -- a top investment bank upgraded its recommendation on the stock and cranked its price target higher.  The finance sector mainstay in question was Goldman Sachs.  Well before market open, its analyst, James Schneider, flipped his recommendation on Accenture stock to buy from his preceding neutral.
